you need not have to activate environment. 
just install django, and apps, you are set

To collect staticfils
first go to project folder. then
/www/wwwroot/prottashaschool.com/80e9fc22001cd7b0808ebebb9aee76d6_venv/bin/python3 manage.py collectstatic
/www/wwwroot/prottashaschool.com/80e9fc22001cd7b0808ebebb9aee76d6_venv/bin/python3 manage.py makemigrations
/www/wwwroot/prottashaschool.com/80e9fc22001cd7b0808ebebb9aee76d6_venv/bin/python3 manage.py migrate


add this to domain config

location / {
    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8001;
    proxy_set_header Host $host;
    proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
}
location /static/ {
    alias /www/wwwroot/prottashaschool.com/staticfiles/;
}

location /media/ {
    alias /www/wwwroot/prottashaschool.com/media/;
}


#add these lines for csrf token in any location {}
proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Host $host;
proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

মূলত এডমিন প্যানেল আসছে উপরের দুই লাইন কোড ও সার্ভার রিসেট এর মাধ্যমে। 



and must use: 

# to show nginx configation file
cat /www/server/panel/vhost/nginx/prottashaschool.com.conf


STATIC_URL = '/static/'
STATICFILES_DIRS = [BASE_DIR / 'static']
STATIC_ROOT = BASE_DIR / 'staticfiles'
